*Sredimo* sve stvari u sobi (Let's tidy up all the things in the room). 

Molim te, *sredi* mi stvari na stole (Please, tidy up the things on the table).

Idemo da *sredimo* nju (Let's tidy her up). 

Idem da *sredim* ovu sobu (I'm going to tidy up this room). 

